# Prompt Organizer

This is a React application for organizing and managing AI prompts with the following features:
- Save, edit, and delete prompts
- Add tags to prompts for categorization
- Search and filter prompts
- Local storage (IndexedDB) for persistence

## Core Files

- Entry point: [src/main.tsx](mdc:src/main.tsx)
- Main application: [src/App.tsx](mdc:src/App.tsx)
- Component definitions: [src/components/PromptModal.tsx](mdc:src/components/PromptModal.tsx)
- Database configuration: [src/db.ts](mdc:src/db.ts)
- Type definitions: [src/types.ts](mdc:src/types.ts)

## Technology Stack

- React (with TypeScript)
- Tailwind CSS for styling
- Dexie.js (IndexedDB wrapper) for local storage
- Vite for build and development
